trait mycrate::AsyncRead

pub trait AsyncRead

Read bytes from a source asynchronously.

Required Methods:
  fn poll_read(self: Pin<&mut Self>, cx: &mut Context<'_>) -> Poll<Result<()>>  Attempts to read from the source.

Provided Methods:
  fn chain<R>(self, next: R) -> Chain<Self, R>                Creates an adaptor which chains this stream.
  fn take(self, limit: u64) -> Take<Self>                     Creates an adaptor which reads at most limit bytes.
